="fi-voteup-arrow"></i><span class="count">41</span><span class="sr-only">赞同</span></button><button class="down" title="反对，不会显示你的姓名"><i class="fi-votedown-arrow"></i><span class="sr-only">反对，不会显示你的姓名</span></button></div></div><div class="entry-body"><div class="entry-meta"><strong class="author-line"><a class="author" href="/people/pan-jun-shen" data-hovercard='p$t$pan-jun-shen'>潘彼得</a>，<span title="菊花航空787机型飞行员" class="bio">菊花航空787机型飞行员</span></strong></div><div class="entry-content js-collapse-body" data-author-name="潘彼得" data-entry-url="/question/60024794/answer/174355743"><div class="summary hidden-expanded js-expand">一般来说是这样的 但是我师父的风格是： 1.今天怎么状态不好？飞成这个样子……算了我来飞吧…… 2.你还是学一下吧你想累死为师吗？！ 3.（螺旋）来我先给给你演示一个啊~ （改出之后）哈哈哈有没有被吓到啊？~ 4.（我一点不怕而且飞螺旋飞上瘾之后）要不我…<a class="toggle-expand inline" href="/question/60024794/answer/174355743">显示全部</a></div><div class="visible-expanded"><div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="41"><span class="voters"><span class="member"><a href="/people/shui-gui-72-58" data-hovercard='p$t$shui-gui-72-58'>水鬼</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/jacky-16-35" data-hovercard='p$t$jacky-16-35'>jacky</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/abujikawayne" data-hovercard='p$t$abujikawayne'>abujikawayne</a></span></span> <a class="more">等人赞同</a></div><script type="text" class="content">一般来说是这样的<figure><img data-rawwidth="650" data-rawheight="800" src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-c67a7ec6bec824935a35659fed627918_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="650" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-c67a7ec6bec824935a35659fed627918_r.jpg"></figure><br>但是我师父的风格是：<br>1.今天怎么状态不好？飞成这个样子……算了我来飞吧……<br>2.你还是学一下吧你想累死为师吗？！<br>3.（螺旋）来我先给给你演示一个啊~<br>（改出之后）哈哈哈有没有被吓到啊？~<br>4.（我一点不怕而且飞螺旋飞上瘾之后）要不我们回去吧今天差不多了（抱头假装晕了）<br><br>……<br>……<br>……<br>不愿意停飞每一个徒儿的师父，买零食给飞机组（学生机长训练）徒儿的师父，每年过年给徒儿发红包的师父，永远与徒儿们打成一片吃肉喝酒的师父~<br>可能这辈子的运气都用来碰见这样的师父了<br><br>另外不要私信问我师父是谁啦~他老人家已经不收徒弟啦~你们死心吧啦啦啦</script><a class="time" href="/question/60024794/answer/174355743">2017-05-25</a></div></div></div></article><div class="item-footer js-contentActions"><ul class="item-actions"><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop"><button class="button-text vote-num js-openVoteDialog"><span data-bind-votecount>41</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text follow unfollowing" data-follow="q:fi:button" data-id="16233032"><i class="fi fi-follow"></i><span class="label">关注</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text comment js-toggleCommentBox toggle-comment"><i class="fi fi-comment"></i><span class="label">18 条评论</span></button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-thank "><i class="fi fi-thank"></i>感谢</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-share"><i class="fi fi-share"></i>分享</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-collect"><i class="fi fi-fav"></i>收藏</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-report"><i class="fi fi-report"></i>举报</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><meta name="copyrightStatus" content="1"><meta name="disableCopyAvatar" content="https://pic2.zhimg.com/1812f7b1f64d6c9a8bcab08f16387ce7_m.jpg"><meta name="own" content="true"><a href="/terms#sec-licence-1" target="_blank" class="action-item js-copyright">作者保留权利</a></li><li class="hidden-phone item-collapse js-collapse"><button class="button-text"><i class="sprite-global-icon-fold-round-default"></i>收起</button></li><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop phone-actions"><button class="button-text menubutton"><i class="fi fi-3-dot"></i>更多</button><div class="menu goog-menu goog-menu-vertical zh-answer-more-actions" style="display:none"><div class="goog-menuitem js-share">分享</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem js-collect">收藏</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem js-thank ">感谢</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem js-report">举报</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem"><meta name="copyrightStatus" content="1"><meta name="disableCopyAvatar" content="https://pic2.zhimg.com/1812f7b1f64d6c9a8bcab08f16387ce7_m.jpg"><a href="/terms#sec-licence-1" target="_blank" class="js-copyright">作者保留权利</a></div></div></li></ul></div></li><li class="item" data-type="Answer"><a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-71722147"></a><link itemprop="url" href="/question/65226218/answer/229083921"><meta itemprop="question-id" content="18316927"><meta itemprop="question-url-token" content="65226218"><meta itemprop="answer-id" content="71722147"><meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="229083921"><div class="item-header"><h2 class="item-title"><a class="js-title-link" target="_blank" href="/question/65226218/answer/229083921">如何看待民航新的招飞标准极大放宽并且允许激光手术？</a></h2></div><article class="entry answer"><div class="entry-left hidden-phone"><a class="rating hidden-expanded js-expand js-vote-count" data-bind-votecount>80</a><div class="votebar visible-expanded"><button class="up " title="赞同"><i class="fi-voteup-arrow"></i><span class="count">80</span><span class="sr-only">赞同</span></button><button class="down" title="反对，不会显示你的姓名"><i class="fi-votedown-arrow"></i><span class="sr-only">反对，不会显示你的姓名</span></button></div></div><div class="entry-body"><div class="entry-meta"><strong class="author-line"><a class="author" href="/people/pan-jun-shen" data-hovercard='p$t$pan-jun-shen'>潘彼得</a>，<span title="菊花航空787机型飞行员" class="bio">菊花航空787机型飞行员</span></strong></div><div class="entry-content js-collapse-body" data-author-name="潘彼得" data-entry-url="/question/65226218/answer/229083921"><div class="summary hidden-expanded js-expand">今天正好有个小朋友问我，简单回答下 这是个满怀飞行梦想的小朋友，可惜我国像他一样的小朋友太多了 民航局新颁布的《民用航空招收飞行学生体检鉴定规范》降低了对招飞的视力要求，我简单归纳了一下，大概有三点： 1.裸眼视力（c字）由0.3放宽到0.1 2.近视…<a class="toggle-expand inline" href="/question/65226218/answer/229083921">显示全部</a></div><div class="visible-expanded"><div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="80"><span class="voters"><span class="member"><a href="/people/wang-xiao-mei-91" data-hovercard='p$t$wang-xiao-mei-91'>九歌</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/fei-tai-lang-shi-jia-fei-xing-yuan" data-hovercard='p$t$fei-tai-lang-shi-jia-fei-xing-yuan'>人才</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/mou-mou-mou-52-60" data-hovercard='p$t$mou-mou-mou-52-60'>和园啧</a></span></span> <a class="more">等人赞同</a></div><script type="text" class="content"><p>今天正好有个小朋友问我，简单回答下<figure><img data-rawheight="1857" src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-1a73e430c17ed48cd61423708b7cd4b0_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1098" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1098" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-1a73e430c17ed48cd61423708b7cd4b0_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img data-rawheight="1080" src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-e4c6369c1be69082806104f8ae29a5ed_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1093" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1093" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-e4c6369c1be69082806104f8ae29a5ed_r.jpg"></figure></p><br><br><figure><img data-rawheight="1835" src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-1419578f180be7ca254faf069584b2f7_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1095" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1095" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-1419578f180be7ca254faf069584b2f7_r.jpg"></figure><br>这是个满怀飞行梦想的小朋友，可惜我国像他一样的小朋友太多了<br><br>民航局新颁布的《民用航空招收飞行学生体检鉴定规范》降低了对招飞的视力要求，我简单归纳了一下，大概有三点：<br>1.裸眼视力（c字）由0.3放宽到0.1<br>2.近视度数由300放宽到450<br>3.做过激光手术的也能报考<br><br>眼科作为以前最主要的筛检科目标准大幅放宽，符合招生需求的生源数量大幅增加。更改后的规定更加接近当前的国际的主流民航招飞惯例（比如说美国）<br><br>民航飞行员不需要像军用飞行员一样卓绝的身体条件，需要更多的是对航空器的管理，对机组资源的管理和运行经验的积累；而这些东西，一般人在经过专业训练和长时间积累经验后都能做到<br><br>所以哪有什么“天之骄子”，能在之前成为飞行员现在又来说教的我们，只是在当年沾着政策便宜幸运的普通人罢了<br><br>回到主题<br><br>看似放开了条件，让更多有着蓝天梦的少年有了圆梦的机会，但这梦圆得真不容易<br><br>这两年经济不景气，好多行业都是艰难度日，能像民航业一样保持发展的行业不多；民航业中，又以飞行员最为光鲜：较高的收入，较高的社会地位，影视作品不断的美化（我说的就是冲上云霄），让大众对这个行业的憧憬与日俱增，怀揣着蓝天梦的少年们更是前仆后继<br><br>我进航校之后的这几年，招飞的分数线从二本以下20％（大概400左右）提到了差不多快600分，公司选拔标准已经大大提升，这次扩宽了招生范围，报名人数无疑继续暴增，分数线也会划得更高，以前因为硬指标过不去而不能参与招飞的内部关系户也得到了新的机会<br><br>现在，你还觉得你是那个万里挑一的幸运儿吗？<br><br>当然，有机会总是比没机会来的好，所以努力学习吧少年们，万一成了呢~<br><br>祝衷心热爱蓝天的诸君都能梦想成真，我们天上见！<br><figure><img data-rawwidth="1242" data-rawheight="819" src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-c01ed43d5260ec638819bcf0731eadd4_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1242" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-c01ed43d5260ec638819bcf0731eadd4_r.jpg"></figure><br><br>ps.另外贴两篇以前写的东西<br>有些问题就不要私信反复问我啦！<br>菊花航空飞航班！很忙的！<br><br><p><a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/31547839/answer/52396648" class="internal">潘彼得：飞行员的真实生活是怎样的？</a></p><p><a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/41681330/answer/92058846" class="internal">潘彼得：为什么飞行员的收入水平那么高，录取分数线却很低？</a></p></script><a class="time" href="/question/65226218/answer/229083921">2017-09-12</a></div></div></div></article><div class="item-footer js-contentActions"><ul class="item-actions"><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop"><button class="button-text vote-num js-openVoteDialog"><span data-bind-votecount>80</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text follow unfollowing" data-follow="q:fi:button" data-id="18316927"><i class="fi fi-follow"></i><span class="label">关注</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text comment js-toggleCommentBox toggle-comment"><i class="fi fi-comment"></i><span class="label">63 条评论</span></button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-thank "><i class="fi fi-thank"></i>感谢</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-share"><i class="fi fi-share"></i>分享</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-collect"><i class="fi fi-fav"></i>收藏</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-report"><i class="fi fi-report"></i>举报</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><meta name="copyrightStatus" content="1"><meta name="disableCopyAvatar" content="https://pic2.zhimg.com/1812f7b1f64d6c9a8bcab08f16387