"><a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-91532093"></a><link itemprop="url" href="/question/268411482/answer/338088606"><meta itemprop="question-id" content="21797955"><meta itemprop="question-url-token" content="268411482"><meta itemprop="answer-id" content="91532093"><meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="338088606"><div class="item-header"><h2 class="item-title"><a class="js-title-link" target="_blank" href="/question/268411482/answer/338088606">成为飞行员一般有哪些途径？「养成生」、「大改驾」「大毕改」这些都是什么意思？</a></h2></div><article class="entry answer"><div class="entry-left hidden-phone"><a class="rating hidden-expanded js-expand js-vote-count" data-bind-votecount>3</a><div class="votebar visible-expanded"><button class="up " title="赞同"><i class="fi-voteup-arrow"></i><span class="count">3</span><span class="sr-only">赞同</span></button><button class="down" title="反对，不会显示你的姓名"><i class="fi-votedown-arrow"></i><span class="sr-only">反对，不会显示你的姓名</span></button></div></div><div class="entry-body"><div class="entry-meta"><strong class="author-line"><a class="author" href="/people/pan-jun-shen" data-hovercard='p$t$pan-jun-shen'>潘彼得</a>，<span title="菊花航空787机型飞行员" class="bio">菊花航空787机型飞行员</span></strong></div><div class="entry-content js-collapse-body" data-author-name="潘彼得" data-entry-url="/question/268411482/answer/338088606"><div class="summary hidden-expanded js-expand">简而言之： 养成生——高中毕业直接与航空公司签约，进入民航院校就读飞行专业 大改驾——大学生与航空公司签约，转入民航院校改读飞行专业，多为1+3或2+2 大毕改——大学毕业后与航空公司签约，回炉再造再回民航院校学习飞行专业<a class="toggle-expand inline" href="/question/268411482/answer/338088606">显示全部</a></div><div class="visible-expanded"><div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="3"><span class="voters"><span class="member"><a href="/people/E.com" data-hovercard='p$t$E.com'>thomasTTyQzYl</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/xiao-fang-78-33" data-hovercard='p$t$xiao-fang-78-33'>小房</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/lonly-man" data-hovercard='p$t$lonly-man'>lonely man</a></span></span> <span>赞同</span></div><script type="text" class="content">简而言之：<br><br>养成生——高中毕业直接与航空公司签约，进入民航院校就读飞行专业<br><br>大改驾——大学生与航空公司签约，转入民航院校改读飞行专业，多为1+3或2+2<br><br>大毕改——大学毕业后与航空公司签约，回炉再造再回民航院校学习飞行专业</script><a class="time" href="/question/268411482/answer/338088606">2018-03-10</a></div></div></div></article><div class="item-footer js-contentActions"><ul class="item-actions"><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop"><button class="button-text vote-num js-openVoteDialog"><span data-bind-votecount>3</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text follow unfollowing" data-follow="q:fi:button" data-id="21797955"><i class="fi fi-follow"></i><span class="label">关注</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text comment js-toggleCommentBox toggle-comment"><i class="fi fi-comment"></i><span class="label">1 条评论</span></button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-thank "><i class="fi fi-thank"></i>感谢</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-share"><i class="fi fi-share"></i>分享</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-collect"><i class="fi fi-fav"></i>收藏</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-report"><i class="fi fi-report"></i>举报</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><meta name="copyrightStatus" content="1"><meta name="disableCopyAvatar" content="https://pic2.zhimg.com/1812f7b1f64d6c9a8bcab08f16387ce7_m.jpg"><meta name="own" content="true"><a href="/terms#sec-licence-1" target="_blank" class="action-item js-copyright">作者保留权利</a></li><li class="hidden-phone item-collapse js-collapse"><button class="button-text"><i class="sprite-global-icon-fold-round-default"></i>收起</button></li><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop phone-actions"><button class="button-text menubutton"><i class="fi fi-3-dot"></i>更多</button><div class="menu goog-menu goog-menu-vertical zh-answer-more-actions" style="display:none"><div class="goog-menuitem js-sh